reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is the best set of travel bottles I’ve had. No leakage. Excellent size. I would get them again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little set!
reviews.reviewText: I initially questioned my purchase when this little set arrived but it worked great. I took a 9 day trip and I had enough toiletries to last me through the trip. There was enough containers to take everything I wanted and nothing leaked. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for your Traveling Needs
reviews.reviewText: To start, I've gone through plenty of these during my trips as most that I have came across do not last as long, or they start to leak within the first time. I was looking for something that I could use for serums, lotions, sprays, shampoos, conditioners, and face wash and glad I came across this. I couldn't pass this up for the price in addition to it including everything we needed.It comes conveniently in a toiletry pouch that is easy to clean and fits everything in it. It even includes a plastic scoop to help you scoop up your creams into the dispenser easier. I also love how it had the labels already and you just need to stick it on. If there isn't a label, you can just easily write it out on the extra blank labels it comes with.So far, we have used this for at least 4 trips in our luggage and it still works just as good. The labels do come off after some time, but that's an easy fix. All the items are still in tact, durable, great quality and easy to clean if you just need to rinse and put in other items, or just refill it.It is perfect for the whole family!
